{"tid":1534251,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"鏗鏘集：這一年......十五歲的暑假","createTime":"2019-09-03T02:56:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:28:57.000Z","uid":144262,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2acc040e9e34345c749b8bfdfd7741fb1a448d80","tid":1534251,"uid":144262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:56:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zXOC0yxGTA0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzXOC0yxGTA0&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFANVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=558fd8bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zXOC0yxGTA0</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可記得不忘初心點解咁重要<br />\n<br />\n如果輸咗 後生嗰班正式玩完"},{"pid":"11ccd57ed7f6a8cd24fc77fb198ea74d43a2a4eb","tid":1534251,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:57:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我唔想知佢錄音內容<br />\n我推到同溫層既大家知道<br />\n你地負責幫手去fb啊等等宣傳得唔得<br />\n唔好再理膠post喇 關注返行動post<br />\n再好好運用6月至今每個核彈去twitter做文宣喇<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFANVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=d57a08f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，<br />\n請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n-大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n-高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n-高舉大量國旗<br />\n-唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼 補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n-領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n無人申請不反 908都要照上街<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"7a1e7ed39102f0f02548d4be5768a1110ee51138","tid":1534251,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:57:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8！到時見！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"h